> ### Name: is_series
> ### Title: Check if an object is treated as a numeric series
> ### Aliases: is_series
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> is_series(natural0())
[1] TRUE
> is_series(c(1, 2, 3))
[1] TRUE
> is_series("not a numeric series")
[1] FALSE
> 
> 
