> 
> ### Name: next_discrete
> ### Title: Traversing a numeric series
> ### Aliases: next_discrete prev_discrete
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> x <- integers(from = 2)
> next_discrete(x, from = 1.3)
[1] 2
> prev_discrete(x, from = 4, n = 10)
[1] 3 2
> next_discrete(x - 0.7, from = 1.3, n = 4)
[1] 2.3 3.3 4.3 5.3
> 
