> ### Name: num_discretes
> ### Title: Number of discrete values in a series
> ### Aliases: num_discretes
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> num_discretes(-3:3)
[1] 7
> num_discretes(c(0.4, 0.4, 0.4, 0))
[1] 2
> 
> x <- arithmetic(-3.2, spacing = 0.5)
> num_discretes(x)
[1] Inf
> num_discretes(x, from = -2, to = 2)
[1] 8
> num_discretes(1 / x, from = -2, to = 2)
[1] Inf
